comment_data.body: @EA-YOUHOU do you have a file `jxbrowser.log` if you go to Help > Show log in finder ? It may help us if you can attach that here or send to me.

[jxbrowser.log](https://github.com/flutter/flutter-intellij/files/8467818/jxbrowser.log)


> @EA-YOUHOU do you have a file `jxbrowser.log` if you go to Help > Show log in finder ? It may help us if you can attach that here or send to me.
Thanks, I'll forward this along to the Jx Browser team.

@EA-YOUHOU the JxBrowser team suggested that this error may occur when we try to open a browser in a space with 0 width/height. At the time that this error occurred, do you recall if the Flutter Inspector tab on the right of the IDE was open?
Didn't know exactly when this error occur. I can't affirm that sorry :/
I'm going to leave this issue open in the hopes that someone else will have this issue and report more information about the status of the inspector tab
